summary: You Followed the Sign of the Wolf Now Follow the Sign of Darkness
descriptionHtml:
It is the second part to the Shadowcasters Race

Shadowcasters who follow the Sign of Darkness are call Dark Shadowcasters these people have little magicka but thank to they Dark Lord Hellforge can cast following without magicka cost. 

Spell: Hell Storm
Spell: Hell Flames
Spell: Soul Bow
Spell: Soul Sword
Power: Dark Seduction

And can resist Fire with Lord Hellforge Blessing 

This is the beta version of the race

Sorry about the spelling

N737
